text: Her swutelað on þisum gewrite þæt Eadsi arcebisceop hæfð geunnan Gode & sancte AugustineVæcera landes butan reada gatan & þa mæda wiðutan Wiwergatan þe þarto lið unawendedlice for his sawle on þa forwyrd ðæt þa gebroðra him beon holde on heora gebedum ægþer ge on life ge æfter life swa hy him behatan habbað.

Nu is ðises to gewitnesse, Godwine biscop on Rofeceastra & Godwine biscop æt sancte Martine & Godric decanus & eall se hired æt Christes cyrcean & Leofwine preost & eall se hired on Doferan & Ægelric bicga & Esbearn & Ægelwine Ælfelmes sunu & þurgar & Eadric æt Æþelham & Eadwine þæs arcebiscop broðor & Ælfwine se reada & Godric æt Burnan & Ælfred & his broðor Gyldewine & seo burwara eall on Cantwarabyrig & þarto manig god mann ægðer ge binnan byrig ge buton.
Nu synd ðissa gewrita twa, an is æt Christes cyrcean, oþer æt sancte Augustine.
